&lt;figcaption class="xCodeBlock_title">WA-Gap Dn Bar&lt;/figcaption>
&lt;div class="xCodeBlock_code">&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-plain" data-lang="plain">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">{ Search Tag: WA-Gap Dn Bar }
